System Requirements
OS: Windows 10/11 (required - uses Win32 APIs)
Python: 3.8+ (you have 3.14.3)
Admin Privileges: Required for full functionality (UAC elevation built-in)


# 1. Create virtual environment
python -m venv venv

# 2. Install core dependencies (guaranteed to work)
venv\Scripts\pip install customtkinter Pillow psutil WMI loguru pywin32

# 3. Optional: Install data science packages (requires Visual Studio Build Tools)
venv\Scripts\pip install numpy pandas scikit-learn scipy

venv\Scripts\pip install -r requirements.txt